**Follow this link https://dgpu-docs.intel.com/driver/client/overview.html**
and install all the given commands

- install python and run this command "sudo apt update" and "sudo apt install python3.12-venv"
- create a virtual environment using python by writting the following command: python3 -m venv <location>/<foldername>
- start the virtual environment using source location/foldername/bin/activate
- then the activated virtual environment run the following commands: "pip install --upgrade pip", "pip install intel-extension-for-pytorch[xpu]" and "pip3 install torch torchvision torchaudio --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/xpu"

```python
